[The St. Clair River drains Lake Huron into Lake St Clair and forms
part of the boundary between the Canadian province of Ontario and the
US state of Michigan. The area can be seen on the
HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map available at
<http://healthmap.org/promed?v=55.4,-101.9,4> - CopyEd.MJ]
